OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779987954
OL,3,CMan who murdered cousin with axe
OL,4,Cjailed for life
OL,6,FA man found guilty of murdering his
OL,7,Fcousin with an axe in East Sussex has
OL,8,Fbeen jailed for life.
OL,10,FDonald Excell, 49, "fatally wounded"
OL,11,F58-year-old Rita Lambourne at an
OL,12,Faddress in Bayencourt South, Bexhill,
OL,13,FEast Sussex, on February 12, 2025.
OL,15,FExcell, of Seabourne Road, Bexhill,
OL,16,Fwas convicted of her murder at Hove
OL,17,FCrown Court last December. He was also
OL,18,Ffound guilty of having an offensive
OL,19,Fweapon in a public place.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
