PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779987954
OL,3,CMan who murdered cousin with axe
OL,4,Cjailed for life
OL,6,FToday, he was handed a life sentence
OL,7,Fwith a minimum of 31 years behind bars.
OL,9,FExcell went into the house through an
OL,10,Funlocked back door before striking Ms
OL,11,FLambourne with an axe at least four
OL,12,Ftimes.
OL,14,FFor the majority of the murder
OL,15,Finvestigation, police were unable to
OL,16,Ffind the axe, or the clothes the
OL,17,Fkiller was seen wearing on CCTV.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
