FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779987954
OL,3,CMan who murdered cousin with axe
OL,4,Cjailed for life
OL,6,FIn September 2025, teenagers fishing
OL,7,Fjust north of Bexhill found a rucksack
OL,8,Fin the water with clothes and the
OL,9,Fsheath of an axe weighed down with a
OL,10,Fsandbag.
OL,12,FDuring the trial, the court heard that
OL,13,FMs Lambourne had been on the phone
OL,14,Fwith her partner moments before the
OL,15,Fattack, and that he heard shouts as
OL,16,Fshe dropped her phone.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779987954
OL,3,CMan who murdered cousin with axe
OL,4,Cjailed for life
OL,6,FHe called Ms Lambourne's daughter
OL,7,FLucy, who in turn called her aunt -
OL,8,Fand Ms Lambourne's sister - Claire
OL,9,FHaldane, to go and check on Ms
OL,10,FLambourne.
OL,12,FMs Haldane discovered her sister in
OL,13,Fthe front room of her house and
OL,14,Fstarted CPR.
OL,16,FLucy Lambourne remembered her aunt
OL,17,Fsaying: "Oh my god, you need to get
OL,18,Fdown here, mum's been smashed up,
OL,19,Flove, call an ambulance."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
