PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779987954
OL,3,CMan who murdered cousin with axe
OL,4,Cjailed for life
OL,6,FSussex Police Detective Chief
OL,7,FInspector Alex Campbell described the
OL,8,Fcase as "extremely distressing",
OL,9,Fadding the sentence "reflects the
OL,10,Fseriousness of Excell's actions".
OL,12,FHe said: "We hope this outcome
OL,13,Fprovides some measure of closure for
OL,14,Fthose who loved Rita.
OL,16,F"Our thoughts remain firmly with her
OL,17,Ffamily, and we thank them for their
OL,18,Fcourage, patience and dignity
OL,19,Fthroughout this incredibly difficult
OL,20,Ftime."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
